# React Component Conventions

Use these defaults:
- Prefer named exports.
- Use the right route guard in `src/App.tsx`: `ProtectedRoute`, `AdminRoute`, `ModuleRoute`.
- Use `useEffectivePermissions` for role-gated UI checks.
- Handle loading/error explicitly (`LoadingSpinner`, `EmptyState`).
- Use shadcn/ui components from `@/components/ui` first.
- Keep Supabase calls in hooks, not components/pages.
- Keep form schemas in `src/lib/validation.ts`.
- For loan features, reuse existing `src/components/loans/*` patterns before adding new component types.
